---
---

<section id="about" class="section" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">

      <div class="about-copy reveal">
        <div class="eyebrow">The ReadyStack Approach</div>
        <h2 id="about-heading" class="section-h2">
          Enterprise-grade web, M365 and security<br>
          <span class="text-amber">practices, priced for small business.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="body-copy">
          Most small business websites are built once, launched in a hurry, and quietly break over the next two years. Forms stop sending. SSL certificates lapse. Plugins bloat. Search rankings slip. Meanwhile, email deliverability suffers because SPF, DKIM and DMARC were never configured, and Microsoft 365 sits insecure with no MFA enforced and no hardening applied.
        </p>
        <p class="body-copy">
          ReadyStack Digital was built to fix that pattern. We combine the same technical practices large organisations use — static-first website architecture, proper DNS and email authentication, Microsoft 365 hardening, Essential Eight Maturity Level 1 alignment, and monitored monthly care — and apply them to small businesses at small business prices. Sydney-based, Australia-wide.
        </p>

        <div class="pillars">
          <div class="pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
                <path d="M11 2L2 6.5v5C2 16.5 5.75 21 11 22.5 16.25 21 20 16.5 20 11.5v-5L11 2z" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.5" fill="rgba(245,158,11,.08)"/>
                <path d="M8 11.5l2 2 4-4" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3>Built right the first time</h3>
              <p>Fast static-first websites with HTTPS, clean DNS, schema markup, and no unnecessary plugins. Microsoft 365 tenants configured properly — custom domain, MFA enforced, Teams and OneDrive set up — from the very first day.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
                <rect x="3" y="5" width="16" height="12" rx="3" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.5" fill="rgba(245,158,11,.08)"/>
                <path d="M4 7l7 5 7-5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3>Secured by default</h3>
              <p>SPF, DKIM, DMARC and MTA-STS configured so your email lands in the inbox. Essential Eight Maturity Level 1 controls applied to your Microsoft 365 environment — application control, patching baselines, hardened tenant, conditional access. The security work most providers skip.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
                <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="9" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.5" fill="rgba(245,158,11,.08)"/>
                <path d="M11 7v4l2.5 2.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3>Managed for the long term</h3>
              <p>Monthly care that actually checks things: website hosting, domain renewal, SSL, form delivery, Microsoft 365 user lifecycle, MFA review, DMARC reports, and Essential Eight monitoring. Real maintenance across your full digital stack — not an invoice in exchange for silence.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-amber magnetic">
          <span>Get a Quote</span>
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M3 8h10M8 3l5 5-5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="about-visual reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="terminal-card">
          <div class="terminal-chrome" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="terminal-dot td-red"></span>
            <span class="terminal-dot td-amber"></span>
            <span class="terminal-dot td-green"></span>
            <span class="terminal-filename">readystack-presence-check.sh</span>
          </div>
          <div class="terminal-body" id="terminal-output" aria-live="polite" aria-label="Website, email and security status output">
            <!-- Typewriter injected by animations.js -->
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-stat-grid">
          <div class="about-stat reveal">
            <div class="about-stat-num" data-count="5" data-suffix="">0</div>
            <div class="about-stat-lbl">Core Setup Areas</div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <div class="about-stat-num" data-count="100" data-suffix="%">0</div>
            <div class="about-stat-lbl">SEO Basics Included</div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <div class="about-stat-num" data-count="0" data-suffix="">0</div>
            <div class="about-stat-lbl">Plugin Bloat</div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat reveal reveal-delay-3">
            <div class="about-stat-num" data-count="30" data-suffix="min">0</div>
            <div class="about-stat-lbl">Monthly Care Allowance</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
